-- my-ds.page.body:

`doc-site` have inbuilt provision of adding `right-sidebar` for additional
components to be shown on right-side of `page` component. 

Add `sidebar: true` attribute to your `page` component.

-- ds.h3: How to enable right-sidebar?

Just copy and paste below code into your new `.ftd` file to see right-sidebar in
action.

-- ds.code:
lang: ftd
download: right-sidebar.ftd

\-- ds.page: Using right-sidebar feature
$sidebar: true

\-- ds.page.body:
add some page body here.

\-- ds.page.extra-headers:

\-- ds.h3: Heading in sidebar
You can call any component inside sidebar

\-- ds.code: Code block in sidebar
lang: ftd

\-- ftd.text: Some title here...
role: $inherited.types.copy-large
color: $inherited.colors.text

\-- end: ds.page.extra-headers

\-- end: ds.page

